<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Spit2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Spit,</orth> vb. (partic. <emph>--ed</emph>) to put as on a spit: <cit><quote>infants --ed upon pikes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 3, 38</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>did s. his body upon a rapier's point,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 4.3.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 3, 56</bibl></cit>.
